{
  "texts": [
    "Another direction could be to extend the approach to handle more complex assembly tasks involving multiple pre-assembly steps.",
    "Additionally, it would be interesting to explore the use of additional hyper parameter combinations or of other reinforcement learning algorithms in addition to the applied PPO approach.",
    "Finally, it would be valuable to test the proposed approach on real-world assembly systems to assess its practicality and generalizability.",
    "Therefore, research should focus on embedding the MARL into a digital twin environment providing interfaces to MES, fleet-management software, or a decision support system."
  ]
}